{
  "stem": "8892.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was here in about four weeks, and a family knew each other, again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's on-- he just came back from the Army after four years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he's a-- my uncle and his uncle were just closest friend and pals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And evidently my uncle told him, you're not-- because he was 26 and ready to get married and the war is over so they wanted he should marry.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said, no, you're not marrying anybody till my niece comes out, and he waited for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I was here like four weeks-- no, yeah, it was longer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was here about two months when they finally, at my aunt's house, bring him with his pal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't know Hungarian at all, and my English was still poor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his friend was there-- translator-- and they took me out to the restaurant, and talking, and I did not like the way he was talking.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he was American soldier in Bergen-Belsen, and he saw a lot of thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he saw how wild things were, which, of course, that part I didn't know because I was occupied with my sister constantly.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he had no respect for any of the survivors, and I was terribly insulted, furious with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came home, I told my cousin, you fixed me up with somebody like that you want me to meet.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The poor guy didn't open his mouth so he was-- because he was other side of-- he was at the Persian Gulf in his four years in the Army.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this guy was in Germany as American soldier, a Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
